---

## Run Project

```bash
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```

---

## API Endpoint

```http
GET /predict?lat=12.9716&lon=77.5946
```

Example:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5000/predict?lat=12.9716&lon=77.5946
```

